Question 1) When defining the string resource in the exercise, what was the ID of the title string? 
R.id.string.title
R.string.title
R.id.title

Question 2) Adding the font size parameter to RestaurantName() composable limits it to emit Text of 32sp only.
True 
False

Question 3) How many arguments were passed to the RestaurantNamePreview() function?
One 
None 
Two


**************Answer********************* 
